  "title": "Sales Interior Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>•        0-20% Monthly Performance Related Pay</p><p>•        2% Monthly Medical Allowance</p><p>•        Yearly Salary Increment</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>•        Develop creative interior design concepts tailored to client needs, including space planning, color schemes, furniture, lighting, and material selection.</p><p>•        Produce detailed 2D and 3D drawings, renderings, and presentations for client approval.</p><p>•        Meet with clients to understand their needs, preferences, and budget, and convert enquiries into confirmed sales.</p><p>•        Follow up on marketing-generated leads and manage the sales process from consultation to closing.</p><p>•        Manage project timelines, budgets, and deliverables to ensure client satisfaction.</p><p>•        Stay updated on the latest design trends, materials, and technologies.</p><p>•        Perform ad-hoc duties as required to support the business.</p><p><strong>Qualifications & Requirements:</strong></p><p>•        Creative with strong knowledge of detailed design drawings.</p><p>•        Proficient in AutoCAD, 3D Studio Max or SketchUp, and Adobe Photoshop.</p><p>•        Preferably 1 year or more of relevant experience in interior design and/or sales.</p><p>•        Strong communication and client-facing skills with the ability to close sales effectively.</p><p>•        Ability to work independently and manage multiple projects efficiently.</p><p>•        Experience in a B2C customized product environment is an advantage.</p><p><br />Maxhunt Resource Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 22C1322<br />\nCynthia Lai | Registration No: R25146301</p>",
